          "tz": 240
        },
        "subject": "LU-2488 t10: add crct10 pclmul implementation",
        "message": "LU-2488 t10: add crct10 pclmul implementation\n\nPatch adds crc t10 dif pclmul implementation for user/kernel,\nif pclmulqdq instrucion is unsupported by CPU, kernel use\ncrc_t10dif kernel implementation, user level use crc_t10dif\nfrom libcfs/posix/.\n\nSigned-off-by: Alexander Boyko <alexander_boyko@xyratex.com>\nXyratex-bug-id: MRP-511\nChange-Id: Ia52d4528c0c702f7d876deb635da63eb84d5ecf9\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
